## Processing Patterns

### Batch Processing
```python
# Bronze (append)
bronze_df.write.mode("append").save("/bronze/events")

# Silver (merge for idempotency)
delta_table.merge(silver_df, condition).execute()

# Gold (overwrite or merge)
gold_df.write.mode("overwrite").save("/gold/metrics")
```

### Streaming Processing
```python
# Bronze stream
spark.readStream.format("json").load(stream_source) \
    .writeStream.format("delta").start("/bronze/events")

# Silver stream
spark.readStream.format("delta").load("/bronze/events") \
    .transform(clean_data) \
    .writeStream.format("delta").start("/silver/events")

# Gold stream (aggregations)
spark.readStream.format("delta").load("/silver/events") \
    .groupBy(window("timestamp", "5 minutes"), "country") \
    .agg(count("*")) \
    .writeStream.format("delta").start("/gold/metrics")
```

---

## Best Practices

| Layer | Transformation | Mode | Partitioning | Optimization |
|-------|----------------|------|--------------|--------------|
| **Bronze** | Minimal (add metadata) | Append | By ingestion_date | Auto-compact ON |
| **Silver** | Validate, dedupe, standardize | Merge | By business date | OPTIMIZE weekly |
| **Gold** | Aggregate, denormalize | Overwrite | By metric date | OPTIMIZE + ZORDER |

